   <abstract displayLabel="Description">The Bell &amp; Howell 134 is an 8mm motion picture camera. The lens is Bell &amp; Howell Super Comat 0.5 inch f/1.9-22 with camera speeds of 8-64 frames per second.The Bell &amp; Howell Company was incorporated in 1907 by two projectionists, Donald J. Bell and Albert Summers Howell.</abstract>
